}, {
  "@id" : "https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/DataApp",
  "@type" : [ "http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class" ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment" : [ {
    "@language" : "es",
    "@value" : "Especialización de ids:DataApp para EDAAnOWL. Permite la declaración de requisitos de entrada (hasInputProfile), perfiles de salida (hasOutputProfile) y métricas de rendimiento (hasPerformanceMetric)."
  }, {
    "@language" : "en",
    "@value" : "Specialization of ids:DataApp for EDAAnOWL. Enables declaration of input requirements (hasInputProfile), output profiles (hasOutputProfile), and performance metrics (hasPerformanceMetric)."
  } ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label" : [ {
    "@language" : "es",
    "@value" : "Aplicación de Datos"
  }, {
    "@language" : "en",
    "@value" : "Data App"
  } ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf" : [ {
    "@id" : "https://w3id.org/idsa/core/DataApp"
  } ]
}, {
  "@id" : "https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/DataAsset",
  "@type" : [ "http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class" ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment" : [ {
    "@language" : "es",
    "@value" : "Especializa ids:DataResource para añadir la capa semántica específica de EDAAnOWL. Los perfiles se vinculan mediante ids:representation → dcat:Distribution → hasFieldMapping → mapsToSpecification. Puede vincularse a la DataApp que lo generó usando prov:wasGeneratedBy."
  }, {
    "@language" : "en",
    "@value" : "Specialises ids:DataResource to add the EDAAnOWL domain-specific semantic layer. Profiles are linked via ids:representation → dcat:Distribution → hasFieldMapping → mapsToSpecification. Can be linked to the DataApp that generated it using prov:wasGeneratedBy."
  } ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label" : [ {
    "@language" : "es",
    "@value" : "Activo de Datos"
  }, {
    "@language" : "en",
    "@value" : "Data Asset"
  } ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf" : [ {
    "@id" : "https://w3id.org/idsa/core/DataResource"
  } ]
}, {
  "@id" : "https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/DataConstraint",
  "@type" : [ "http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class" ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment" : [ {
    "@language" : "es",
    "@value" : "Define una restricción de umbral de calidad (p. ej., completitud >= 0.9) para ser utilizada en el matchmaking."
  }, {
    "@language" : "en",
    "@value" : "Defines a quality threshold constraint (e.g., completeness >= 0.9) to be used in matchmaking."
  } ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label" : [ {
    "@language" : "en",
    "@value" : "Data Constraint"
  }, {
    "@language" : "es",
    "@value" : "Restricción de Calidad"
  } ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf" : [ {
    "@id" : "_:genid69"
  }, {
    "@id" : "_:genid70"
  }, {
    "@id" : "_:genid71"
  } ]
}, {
  "@id" : "https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/DataProfile",
  "@type" : [ "http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class" ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment" : [ {
    "@language" : "es",
    "@value" : "Superclase para todos los tipos de perfil en EDAAnOWL. Un DataProfile agrupa una o más DataSpecifications para representar un conjunto de variables semánticas. Las subclases especializan su rol: InputProfile (variables requeridas por una DataApp) y OutputProfile (variables producidas por una DataApp). Use DataProfile directamente cuando el perfil no tiene restricción direccional (p. ej., para una descripción a nivel de Distribution)."
  }, {
    "@language" : "en",
    "@value" : "Superclass for all profile types in EDAAnOWL. A DataProfile groups one or more DataSpecifications to represent a set of semantic variables. Subclasses specialize its role: InputProfile (variables required by a DataApp) and OutputProfile (variables produced by a DataApp). Use DataProfile directly when the profile has no directional constraint (e.g., for a Distribution-level description)."
  } ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label" : [ {
    "@language" : "en",
    "@value" : "Data Profile"
  }, {
    "@language" : "es",
    "@value" : "Perfil de Datos"
  } ]
}, {
  "@id" : "https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/DataRepresentation",
  "@type" : [ "http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class" ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment" : [ {
    "@language" : "en",
    "@value" : "Physical representation of (structured) data. Specializes ids:DataRepresentation \n    from the IDSA taxonomy to add EDAAnOWL-specific semantics for data profiles and quality metrics.\n    \n    Alignment: ids:DataRepresentation extends dcat:Distribution (W3C DCAT 2+), \n    ensuring interoperability with DCAT-based catalogs while maintaining IDSA compliance."
  }, {
    "@language" : "es",
    "@value" : "Representación física de datos (estructurados). Especializa ids:DataRepresentation \n    de la taxonomía IDSA para añadir semántica específica de EDAAnOWL para perfiles de datos y métricas de calidad.\n    \n    Alineación: ids:DataRepresentation extiende dcat:Distribution (W3C DCAT 2+), \n    asegurando interoperabilidad con catálogos basados en DCAT mientras mantiene conformidad IDSA."
  } ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label" : [ {
    "@language" : "en",
    "@value" : "Data Representation"
  }, {
    "@language" : "es",
    "@value" : "Representación de Datos"
  } ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf" : [ {
    "@id" : "https://w3id.org/idsa/core/DataRepresentation"
  } ]
}, {
  "@id" : "https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/DataSpecification",
  "@type" : [ "http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class" ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment" : [ {
    "@language" : "en",
    "@value" : "Atomic and reusable semantic unit that describes WHAT is being observed (Feature of Interest) and WHICH property is measured (Observable Property).\n    \nDataSpecifications are schema-agnostic. They do not contain mapping information (mapsField), units, or technical distribution details (resolutions, CRS), which belong to Distribution, FieldMapping, or explicit constraints."
  }, {
    "@language" : "es",
    "@value" : "Unidad semántica atómica y reutilizable que describe QUÉ se está observando (Feature of Interest) y QUÉ propiedad se mide (Observable Property).\n    \nLos DataSpecifications son ahora independientes del esquema. Ya no contienen información de mapeo (mapsField) ni detalles técnicos de la distribución (resoluciones, CRS), los cuales se han movido a Distribution o FieldMapping."
  } ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label" : [ {
    "@language" : "en",
    "@value" : "Data Specification"
  }, {
    "@language" : "es",
    "@value" : "Perfil de Datos"
  } ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf" : [ {
    "@id" : "http://purl.org/dc/terms/Standard"
  }, {
    "@id" : "_:genid72"
  }, {
    "@id" : "_:genid73"
  } ]
}, {
  "@id" : "https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/Equal",
  "@type" : [ "http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#NamedIndividual" ],
  "http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type" : [ {
    "@id" : "https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/ConstraintOperator"
  } ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel" : [ {
    "@language" : "en",
    "@value" : "Equal"
  }, {
    "@language" : "es",
    "@value" : "Igual"
  } ]
}, {
  "@id" : "https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/FeatureOfInterest",
  "@type" : [ "http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class" ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment" : [ {
    "@language" : "es",
    "@value" : "De lo que se habla o lo que se observa (el objeto real o fenómeno). Ejemplos: una naranja, una parcela, un lote de aceite. RECOMENDADO: Usar SIEX o AGROVOC para clasificar el tipo de objeto."
  }, {
    "@language" : "en",
    "@value" : "The phenomenon or entity being observed or described (the 'thing' itself). Examples: an orange, a plot of land, a batch of oil. RECOMMENDED: Use SIEX or AGROVOC to classify the object type."
  } ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label" : [ {
    "@language" : "es",
    "@value" : "Característica de Interés"
  }, {
    "@language" : "en",
    "@value" : "Feature of Interest"
  } ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf" : [ {
    "@id" : "http://www.w3.org/ns/sosa/FeatureOfInterest"
  } ]
}, {
  "@id" : "https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/FieldMapping",
  "@type" : [ "http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class" ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment" : [ {
    "@language" : "es",
    "@value" : "La clase 'puente' que instancia un DataSpecification reutilizable para un campo específico en una distribución. Mapea el concepto semántico a un identificador físico (mapsField) y proporciona métricas de calidad específicas del campo."
  }, {
    "@language" : "en",
    "@value" : "The 'bridge' class that instantiates a reusable DataSpecification for a specific field in a distribution. It maps the semantic concept to a physical identifier (mapsField) and carries field-level technical details such as unit, data type, observation metric, and quality metrics."
  } ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label" : [ {
    "@language" : "en",
    "@value" : "Field Mapping"
  }, {
    "@language" : "es",
    "@value" : "Vínculo de Perfil"
  } ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf" : [ {
    "@id" : "_:genid74"
  }, {
    "@id" : "_:genid75"
  }, {
    "@id" : "_:genid76"
  } ]
}, {
  "@id" : "https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/GreaterOrEqual",
  "@type" : [ "http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#NamedIndividual" ],
  "http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type" : [ {
    "@id" : "https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/ConstraintOperator"
  } ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel" : [ {
    "@language" : "en",
    "@value" : "Greater or Equal"
  }, {
    "@language" : "es",
    "@value" : "Mayor o Igual"
  } ]
}, {
  "@id" : "https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/GreaterThan",
  "@type" : [ "http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#NamedIndividual" ],
  "http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type" : [ {
    "@id" : "https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/ConstraintOperator"
  } ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel" : [ {
    "@language" : "en",
    "@value" : "Greater Than"
  }, {
    "@language" : "es",
    "@value" : "Mayor que"
  } ]
}, {
  "@id" : "https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/InputProfile",
  "@type" : [ "http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class" ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment" : [ {
    "@language" : "es",
    "@value" : "Subclase de DataProfile. Define un requisito estructurado para un puerto de entrada de DataApp, especificando exactamente qué DataSpecification se necesita y qué umbrales de calidad deben cumplirse mediante DataConstraints."
  }, {
    "@language" : "en",
    "@value" : "Subclass of DataProfile. Defines a structured requirement for a DataApp input port, specifying exactly which DataSpecification is needed and what quality thresholds must be met via DataConstraints."
  } ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label" : [ {
    "@language" : "en",
    "@value" : "Input Profile"
  }, {
    "@language" : "es",
    "@value" : "Perfil de Entrada"
  } ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf" : [ {
    "@id" : "https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/DataProfile"
  }, {
    "@id" : "_:genid77"
  }, {
    "@id" : "_:genid78"
  } ]
}, {
  "@id" : "https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/Instantaneous",
  "@type" : [ "http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#NamedIndividual" ],
  "http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type" : [ {
    "@id" : "https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/ObservationMetric"
  } ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel" : [ {
    "@language" : "en",
    "@value" : "Instantaneous"
  }, {
    "@language" : "es",
    "@value" : "Instantáneo"
  } ]
}, {
  "@id" : "https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/LessOrEqual",
  "@type" : [ "http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#NamedIndividual" ],
  "http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type" : [ {
    "@id" : "https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/ConstraintOperator"
  } ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel" : [ {
    "@language" : "en",
    "@value" : "Less or Equal"
  }, {
    "@language" : "es",
    "@value" : "Menor o Igual"
  } ]
}, {
  "@id" : "https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/LessThan",
  "@type" : [ "http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#NamedIndividual" ],
  "http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type" : [ {
    "@id" : "https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/ConstraintOperator"
  } ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel" : [ {
    "@language" : "en",
    "@value" : "Less Than"
  }, {
    "@language" : "es",
    "@value" : "Menor que"
  } ]
}, {
  "@id" : "https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/Maximum",
  "@type" : [ "http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#NamedIndividual" ],
  "http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type" : [ {
    "@id" : "https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/ObservationMetric"
  } ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel" : [ {
    "@language" : "en",
    "@value" : "Maximum"
  }, {
    "@language" : "es",
    "@value" : "Máximo"
  } ]
}, {
  "@id" : "https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/Metric",
  "@type" : [ "http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class" ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment" : [ {
    "@language" : "en",
    "@value" : "A class representing a single, measurable characteristic (measurement) of an asset or profile. Aligned with dqv:QualityMeasurement. Use :metricType to link to the standardized metric definition (dqv:Metric)."
  }, {
    "@language" : "es",
    "@value" : "Una clase que representa una característica única y medible (medición) de un activo o perfil. Alineada con dqv:QualityMeasurement. Use :metricType para vincular a la definición de métrica estandarizada (dqv:Metric)."
  } ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label" : [ {
    "@language" : "en",
    "@value" : "Metric (Measurement)"
  }, {
    "@language" : "es",
    "@value" : "Métrica (Medición)"
  } ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf" : [ {
    "@id" : "http://www.w3.org/ns/dqv#QualityMeasurement"
  }, {
    "@id" : "_:genid79"
  }, {
    "@id" : "_:genid80"
  } ]
}, {
  "@id" : "https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/MetricType",
  "@type" : [ "http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class" ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment" : [ {
    "@language" : "en",
    "@value" : "A controlled vocabulary term for standardized metric definitions (e.g., completeness, recordCount, cloudCoverage). Aligned with dqv:Metric. RECOMMENDED: Use external vocabularies like DDI (SummaryStatisticType), STATO (Statistical Methods Ontology), or W3C DQV for quality metrics. Use :metricType to link a measurement (:Metric) to its definition."
  }, {
    "@language" : "es",
    "@value" : "Un término de vocabulario controlado para definiciones de métricas estandarizadas (p. ej., completitud, recuento de registros, cobertura de nubes). Alineado con dqv:Metric. RECOMENDADO: Usar vocabularios externos como DDI (SummaryStatisticType), STATO (Statistical Methods Ontology) o W3C DQV para métricas de calidad. Use :metricType para vincular una medición (:Metric) con su definición."
  } ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label" : [ {
    "@language" : "es",
    "@value" : "Definición de Métrica (Tipo)"
  }, {
    "@language" : "en",
    "@value" : "Metric Definition (Type)"
  } ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf" : [ {
    "@id" : "http://www.w3.org/ns/dqv#Metric"
  } ]
}, {
  "@id" : "https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/Minimum",
  "@type" : [ "http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#NamedIndividual" ],
  "http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type" : [ {
    "@id" : "https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/ObservationMetric"
  } ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel" : [ {
    "@language" : "en",
    "@value" : "Minimum"
  }, {
    "@language" : "es",
    "@value" : "Mínimo"
  } ]
}, {
  "@id" : "https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/ObservableProperty",
  "@type" : [ "http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class" ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment" : [ {
    "@language" : "es",
    "@value" : "La variable semántica que describe un activo de datos o que un servicio requiere/produce. RECOMENDADO: Usar AGROVOC para conceptos agrícolas o EuroSciVoc para ciencia general."
  }, {
    "@language" : "en",
    "@value" : "The semantic variable that a data asset describes or a service requires/produces. RECOMMENDED: Use AGROVOC for agricultural concepts or EuroSciVoc for general science."
  } ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label" : [ {
    "@language" : "en",
    "@value" : "Observable Property"
  }, {
    "@language" : "es",
    "@value" : "Propiedad Observable"
  } ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf" : [ {
    "@id" : "http://www.w3.org/ns/sosa/ObservableProperty"
  } ]
}, {
  "@id" : "https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/ObservationMetric",
  "@type" : [ "http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class" ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment" : [ {
    "@language" : "es",
    "@value" : "Métrica estadística o de agregación de la observación (p. ej., MediaDiaria, Máximo, Instantáneo)."
  }, {
    "@language" : "en",
    "@value" : "Statistical or aggregation metric of the observation (e.g., DailyAverage, Maximum, Instantaneous)."
  } ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label" : [ {
    "@language" : "es",
    "@value" : "Métrica de Observación"
  }, {
    "@language" : "en",
    "@value" : "Observation Metric"
  } ]
}, {
  "@id" : "https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/OutputProfile",
  "@type" : [ "http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class" ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment" : [ {
    "@language" : "es",
    "@value" : "Subclase de DataProfile. Define una declaración estructurada para un puerto de salida de DataApp, especificando exactamente qué DataSpecifications produce."
  }, {
    "@language" : "en",
    "@value" : "Subclass of DataProfile. Defines a structured declaration for a DataApp output port, specifying exactly which DataSpecifications it produces."
  } ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label" : [ {
    "@language" : "en",
    "@value" : "Output Profile"
  }, {
    "@language" : "es",
    "@value" : "Perfil de Salida"
  } ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf" : [ {
    "@id" : "https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/DataProfile"
  }, {
    "@id" : "_:genid81"
  } ]
}, {
  "@id" : "https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/PerformanceMetric",
  "@type" : [ "http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class" ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment" : [ {
    "@language" : "en",
    "@value" : "A metric that describes the performance of a DataApp or service (e.g., accuracy, execution time)."
  }, {
    "@language" : "es",
    "@value" : "Una métrica que describe el rendimiento de una DataApp o servicio (p. ej., precisión, tiempo de ejecución)."
  } ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label" : [ {
    "@language" : "es",
    "@value" : "Métrica de Rendimiento"
  }, {
    "@language" : "en",
    "@value" : "Performance Metric"
  } ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf" : [ {
    "@id" : "https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/Metric"
  } ]
}, {
  "@id" : "https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/PredictionApp",
  "@type" : [ "http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class" ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment" : [ {
    "@language" : "en",
    "@value" : "A smart data app that produces predictions/inferences from input data using a model or algorithm."
  }, {
    "@language" : "es",
    "@value" : "Una aplicación de datos inteligente que produce predicciones/inferencias a partir de datos de entrada usando un modelo o algoritmo."
  } ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label" : [ {
    "@language" : "es",
    "@value" : "Aplicación de Predicción"
  }, {
    "@language" : "en",
    "@value" : "Prediction App"
  } ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf" : [ {
    "@id" : "https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/DataApp"
  }, {
    "@id" : "https://w3id.org/idsa/core/SmartDataApp"
  } ]
}, {
  "@id" : "https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/QualityMetric",
  "@type" : [ "http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class" ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment" : [ {
    "@language" : "en",
    "@value" : "A quality metric definition describing a qualitative or quantitative aspect of data quality (e.g., completeness, uniqueness, record count). Aligned with dqv:QualityMetric. Individual measurements belong to :Metric / dqv:QualityMeasurement and should link here via :metricType."
  }, {
    "@language" : "es",
    "@value" : "Una métrica que describe un aspecto cualitativo o cuantitativo de la calidad de datos (p. ej., completitud, unicidad, recuento de registros). Alineada con dqv:QualityMetric."
  } ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label" : [ {
    "@language" : "es",
    "@value" : "Métrica de Calidad"
  }, {
    "@language" : "en",
    "@value" : "Quality Metric"
  } ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf" : [ {
    "@id" : "http://www.w3.org/ns/dqv#QualityMetric"
  }, {
    "@id" : "https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/MetricType"
  } ]
}, {
  "@id" : "https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/QualityReport",
  "@type" : [ "http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class" ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment" : [ {
    "@language" : "en",
    "@value" : "An external, structured quality report containing metadata about a quality assessment (e.g., a PDF report URL, a quality score)."
  }, {
    "@language" : "es",
    "@value" : "Un informe de calidad externo y estructurado que contiene metadatos sobre una evaluación de calidad (p. ej., una URL de informe PDF, una puntuación de calidad)."
  } ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label" : [ {
    "@language" : "es",
    "@value" : "Informe de Calidad"
  }, {
    "@language" : "en",
    "@value" : "Quality Report"
  } ]
}, {
  "@id" : "https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/SpatialTemporalAsset",
  "@type" : [ "http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class" ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment" : [ {
    "@language" : "es",
    "@value" : "Subclase de DataAsset para datos con cobertura espacial y temporal, como datos de Observación de la Tierra."
  }, {
    "@language" : "en",
    "@value" : "Subclass of DataAsset for data with spatial and temporal coverage, such as Earth Observation data."
  } ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label" : [ {
    "@language" : "es",
    "@value" : "Activo Espacio-Temporal"
  }, {
    "@language" : "en",
    "@value" : "Spatial Temporal Asset"
  } ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf" : [ {
    "@id" : "https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/DataAsset"
  } ]
}, {
  "@id" : "https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/Timeliness",
  "@type" : [ "http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#NamedIndividual" ],
  "http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type" : [ {
    "@id" : "https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/MetricType"
  } ],
