    "@language" : "en",
    "@value" : "DEPRECATED: A DataApp implements a Component, not a Workflow.\n\nUse :implementsComponent instead to link a DataApp to the BIGOWL Component it implements.\nA Workflow is a pipeline composed of multiple Components connected via Tasks.\n\nIf you need to indicate workflow membership, consider using bigwf:hasComponent (inverse)."
  }, {
    "@language" : "es",
    "@value" : "OBSOLETO: Una DataApp implementa un Component, no un Workflow.\n\nUse :implementsComponent para vincular una DataApp con el Component BIGOWL que implementa.\nUn Workflow es un pipeline compuesto por múltiples Components conectados via Tasks."
  } ],
